                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">The name of ʿAmdä Mikaʾel is written in the supplication formulas in the main hand. In many cases (esp. at the beginning of the text) his name has been erased and replaced with that of Sǝbḥat Lä-ʾAb. This name is also mentioned in the commemorative notices which were added on blank folios at a later stage (s. Additio 1). &#xD;
